  "body": "<p>Hello! I am excited to be celebrating the release of <a href=\"http://northridgepublishing.com/store/display/signature-series-amy-tan/aid:amytan\">my new Signature Series book</a>! Northridge Publishing will be announcing all the details on the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/northridge.signatureseries\">Signature Series Facebook page</a> each day. There are some awesome prize packs up for grabs from my favorite companies like American Crafts, Fiskars, jillibean soup, and more!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600125190242-M07J5IYSIYD0SUZ4OUB6/17a-amytanlaunch-533x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Thought it would be fun to share <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/galleries/82322-best-day-ever?aff=6cc2c70f\">a page by Jennifer</a>, who said: <em>I scraplifted this idea and layout from Amy Tan's Signature Series book. It was a great way to use up my never ending washi stash! I also used chalkboard spray paint for the 2 word bubbles and arrow. Thanks Amy for the inspiration!</em>Thanks Jen for sharing such a fun page!</p><p>If you happen to already have my book (Jen got <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/studio-selections--2/amy-tan-signature-series-autographed-copy?aff=6cc2c70f\">a signed copy from Studio Calico</a>) and have made something inspired by it, please link up in the comments below. I would love to add it to <a href=\"http://pinterest.com/amytangerine/our-products/\">my Pinterest board</a> and possibly feature you this week!</p><p>Be sure to stop by the <a href=\"http://create.northridgepublishing.com/amy-tan-signature-series-launch-party-day-1/\">Northridge blog</a> as they are giving away 10 copies of my book today - Happy Monday!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}